      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">S060B: Remove fly-tipped rubbish at below-ground geodiversity features</h1>
      <p class="govuk-body-l">How land managers can clear dumped rubbish from protected geological sites, like SSSIs, that are below the ground, and what surveys or licences you need.</p>
    </div>

      <!-- PUBLISHING INFORMATION -->

